 \"My expectation\", \"from\": 752, \"to\": 766}, {\"ngram\": \"the Wuhan Open\", \"from\": 770, \"to\": 784}, {\"ngram\": \"every single match\", \"from\": 817, \"to\": 835}, {\"ngram\": \"Sports Scene's Shen Xiang\", \"from\": 849, \"to\": 874}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Of course, I would like progress as far as I can, so people could watch me more on the tennis court.\", \"from\": 876, \"to\": 977, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"progress\", \"from\": 901, \"to\": 909}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 930, \"to\": 936}, {\"ngram\": \"the tennis court\", \"from\": 960, \"to\": 976}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But you know, no pressure, because I just want to keep myself playing with a calm mood.\", \"from\": 978, \"to\": 1065, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a calm mood\", \"from\": 1053, \"to\": 1064}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And then at the same time to know what I am capable to do, but just focus on every day.\\\"\", \"from\": 1066, \"to\": 1154, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the same time\", \"from\": 1078, \"to\": 1091}, {\"ngram\": \"every day\", \"from\": 1143, \"to\": 1152}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Zheng revealed that she does not spend too much time on social media to avoid distraction.\", \"from\": 1156, \"to\": 1246, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1156, \"end\": 1161, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zheng_Jie\", \"score\": 0.9999984596120652, \"rank\": 1.5390747523569807e-06, \"text\": \"Zheng\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zheng_Jie\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zheng_Jie\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"too much time\", \"from\": 1195, \"to\": 1208}, {\"ngram\": \"social media\", \"from\": 1212, \"to\": 1224}, {\"ngram\": \"distraction\", \"from\": 1234, \"to\": 1245}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am trying to use less social media and to keep myself in the real world instead of on the internet,\\\" she sai